Info.Description: Compila progr que se deben pasar a SICRRAPTEST (nueva KB)

WebPanel.Events:
Event Start PLoadContext.Call(&Context) PIsAuthorized.Call(&Pgmname, &IsAuthorized) If &IsAuthorized = Boolean.False HNotAuthorized.Call(&Pgmname) Endif
&CurrentPage = 1 &CurrentPage.Visible = Boolean.False
Grid1.Rows = Page.Rows &Update = LoadBitmap(!"images/edit.gif") &Update.Tooltiptext = "GXM_update" Form.Caption = 'Trabajar con EMPRESAS'
Do 'PrepareTransaction' EndEvent
Event Refresh Do 'LoadGridState' Do 'FixCurrentPage' EndEvent
Sub 'FixCurrentPage' If Grid1.PageCount = 0 &CurrentPage = 0 Else If &CurrentPage > Grid1.PageCount &CurrentPage = Grid1.PageCount Else If &CurrentPage < 1 &CurrentPage = 1 EndIf EndIf EndIf EndSub
Event Grid1.Load &Update.Link = Link(TEMPRESAS, TrnMode.Update, EMPRNUMEMP) EMPRRAZSOC.Link = Link(HViewEMPRESAS, EMPRNUMEMP, "") EndEvent
/*** Subroutines and events for user interaction. ***/
Event First.Click &CurrentPage = 1 Do 'SaveGridPage' Grid1.FirstPage() EndEvent
Event Previous.Click &CurrentPage = &CurrentPage - 1 Do 'SaveGridPage' Grid1.PreviousPage() EndEvent
Event Next.Click &CurrentPage = &CurrentPage + 1 Do 'SaveGridPage' Grid1.NextPage() EndEvent
Event Last.Click &CurrentPage = Grid1.PageCount Do 'SaveGridPage' Grid1.LastPage() EndEvent
Event 'Search' &CurrentPage = 1 Do 'SaveGridState' Grid1.FirstPage() EndEvent
/*** Subroutines used to load and save the grid state. ***/
Sub 'LoadGridState' If (&HTTPRequest.Method = HttpMethod.Get) // Load grid state from session. &GridState.FromXml(&Session.Get(&PgmName + !"GridState"))
If &GridState.FilterValues.Count >= 1 &EMPRRAZSOC.FromString(&GridState.FilterValues.Item(1).Value) EndIf
If &GridState.CurrentPage > 0 &CurrentPage = &GridState.CurrentPage Grid1.GotoPage(&CurrentPage) EndIf EndIf EndSub
Sub 'SaveGridPage' // Save current page in session. &GridState.FromXml(&Session.Get(&PgmName + !"GridState")) &GridState.CurrentPage = &CurrentPage &Session.Set(&PgmName + !"GridState", &GridState.ToXml()) EndSub
Sub 'SaveGridState' &GridState.FromXml(&Session.Get(&PgmName + !"GridState"))
// Save grid state in session. &GridState.CurrentPage = &CurrentPage &GridState.FilterValues.Clear()
&GridStateFilterValue = new GridState.FilterValue() &GridStateFilterValue.Value = &EMPRRAZSOC.ToString() &GridState.FilterValues.Add(&GridStateFilterValue)
&Session.Set(&PgmName + !"GridState", &GridState.ToXml()) EndSub
Sub 'PrepareTransaction' &TrnContext = new TransactionContext() &TrnContext.CallerObject = &Pgmname &TrnContext.CallerOnDelete = Boolean.True &TrnContext.CallerURL = PLinkTo.Udp(&HTTPRequest) &TrnContext.TransactionName = !"TEMPRESAS"
&Session.Set(!"TrnContext", &TrnContext.ToXml()) EndSub
Event 'Export' // Generate Excel spreadsheet and download it. PExportWWEMPRESAS.Call(&EMPRRAZSOC, &ExcelFilename, &ErrorMessage) If (&ExcelFilename <> "") Link(&ExcelFilename) Else msg(&ErrorMessage) Endif EndEvent
